ï»¿WEBVTT

00:02:14.968 --> 00:02:16.553
Mother

00:02:20.349 --> 00:02:21.725
'Appa...!'

00:02:31.818 --> 00:02:33.362
'Let's kill this boy also. partner'

00:02:33.403 --> 00:02:36.448
If we burn all the evidence
we will be the prime suspects

00:02:36.490 --> 00:02:38.700
'We need a witness
to speak in our favor'

00:02:38.742 --> 00:02:40.077
All that is fine

00:02:40.118 --> 00:02:43.705
Just like his father. what if he also
makes trouble insisting on being truthful?

00:02:44.122 --> 00:02:45.541
Let's find out right away

00:02:45.958 --> 00:02:47.876
Hey boy
What's your name?

00:02:48.460 --> 00:02:49.920
- Bhavani
- Huh?

00:02:50.921 --> 00:02:51.922
Bhavani

00:02:51.964 --> 00:02:53.549
How did your parents die?

00:02:56.593 --> 00:02:58.637
They were burnt to death
in a gas explosion

00:02:58.679 --> 00:03:00.138
[loud laughter]

00:03:02.724 --> 00:03:04.351
He sure knows to survive. I say

00:03:04.393 --> 00:03:05.978
After we use him as a witness

00:03:06.019 --> 00:03:08.730
...let us complain against him
for stealing our union funds

00:03:08.814 --> 00:03:10.399
'His father is Lorry Union leader'

00:03:10.440 --> 00:03:13.110
If we claim his son stole union cash
will anyone believe that story?

00:03:13.151 --> 00:03:15.070
Sudden show of mercy. huh?

00:03:15.112 --> 00:03:17.030
He's so young. that's why

00:03:17.072 --> 00:03:19.032
Hey boy. listen

00:03:20.075 --> 00:03:22.911
I'll send you to a place where boys
like you are well looked after

00:03:22.953 --> 00:03:24.913
Will you go there?

00:03:27.332 --> 00:03:29.960
'Govt Juvenile Observation Home
Nagercoil. Kallakurichi'

00:03:31.879 --> 00:03:34.882
'That boy shouldn't sleep
even one night in peace'

00:03:35.007 --> 00:03:37.009
I've given you more than
what you asked

00:03:37.050 --> 00:03:38.135
Thank you. brother

00:03:38.177 --> 00:03:41.555
If there's any kind of foul play
Esakki will hunt you down and kill you

00:03:41.597 --> 00:03:43.056
- Keep an eye
- I'll take care. bro

00:03:49.479 --> 00:03:50.564
'Hey! Come'

00:03:51.148 --> 00:03:52.900
'What are you glaring at him for?'

00:03:56.820 --> 00:03:59.781
Hey! You want the luxury of sleep. huh?

00:04:04.703 --> 00:04:05.704
What are you looking at?

00:04:05.787 --> 00:04:07.080
Wipe it

00:04:07.122 --> 00:04:08.415
Wipe my boots

00:04:10.375 --> 00:04:12.002
Pickle you to pieces. rascal!

00:04:15.756 --> 00:04:17.382
'All of you. move aside'

00:04:17.424 --> 00:04:18.550
'Bro!'

00:04:22.763 --> 00:04:24.014
Die!

00:04:30.354 --> 00:04:32.689
Hey you! Can't hit you more than this

00:04:33.315 --> 00:04:34.316
Standing

00:04:34.358 --> 00:04:36.151
Standing so still
least bit affected!

00:04:36.318 --> 00:04:38.862
You are hitting me mercilessly
because someone is paying you

00:04:38.904 --> 00:04:42.032
I have to pay you much more
to make you stop hitting me

00:04:42.741 --> 00:04:44.868
I am penniless
Hit me all you want

00:04:44.952 --> 00:04:46.578
When I have the money

00:04:46.620 --> 00:04:47.746
I'll call you then

00:04:56.296 --> 00:04:58.507
[phone ringing]

00:05:03.345 --> 00:05:04.763
- Who is this?
- 'Brother'

00:05:04.805 --> 00:05:06.765
'That boy Bhavani has escaped from jail'

00:05:06.807 --> 00:05:08.934
Scumbag! Is this why
I'm spending so lavishly?

00:05:09.893 --> 00:05:12.896
I'll deal with you in person
Find him before daybreak

00:05:14.189 --> 00:05:15.190
Scumbag!

00:05:29.037 --> 00:05:30.414
'Don't worry. Brother'

00:05:30.455 --> 00:05:31.915
I won't harm you

00:05:31.957 --> 00:05:35.335
'If I had wanted to. I could have easily
slit your neck when you were asleep'

00:05:35.377 --> 00:05:38.714
But I can't be on the run
throughout my life

00:05:38.755 --> 00:05:41.175
I came here to request you
to let me lead a normal life

00:05:41.300 --> 00:05:42.384
I don't understand

00:05:45.053 --> 00:05:46.513
Let me live my own life

00:05:46.555 --> 00:05:48.891
What do I gain by releasing you. huh?

00:05:48.932 --> 00:05:50.976
Give me a chance
for just this 1 week

00:05:51.185 --> 00:05:53.854
I'll give you half of
what I earn this week

00:05:53.896 --> 00:05:55.731
'Whichever week I don't pay you'

00:05:55.731 --> 00:05:57.816
...stab me on that same day
at that same spot

00:05:57.983 --> 00:05:59.985
Fine. I'll take a chance on you

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:02.321
This week is yours. go

00:06:05.365 --> 00:06:08.744
How much do you usually pay for a lorry
to cross the check post without a permit?

00:06:08.785 --> 00:06:11.496
Only if you cough up Rs 1000 per lorry
you'll be allowed to pass

00:06:11.538 --> 00:06:13.290
I'll get the permit slip

00:06:13.332 --> 00:06:15.000
Rs 1000 is yours to keep

00:06:15.375 --> 00:06:16.793
I want Rs 100 per lorry

00:06:17.336 --> 00:06:18.837
If the policemen hassle us?

00:06:21.840 --> 00:06:23.425
That's my responsibility

00:06:32.893 --> 00:06:35.187
What. I say?
What do you want?

00:06:47.950 --> 00:06:50.077
'2002-2003
Register'

00:06:58.794 --> 00:07:00.295
Go...go

00:07:02.506 --> 00:07:03.757
Move...move

00:07:04.550 --> 00:07:05.592
Come. quick

00:07:05.634 --> 00:07:07.094
Hey! Wait...wait

00:07:07.886 --> 00:07:08.887
Hurry up

00:07:13.934 --> 00:07:16.520
If you want the permit slip in your hand

00:07:16.562 --> 00:07:18.689
I must get Rs 500 per lorry

00:07:20.482 --> 00:07:21.733
Got it?

00:07:44.464 --> 00:07:45.591
Whether I'm here or not

00:07:45.632 --> 00:07:48.177
...ensure the boys get
their share of booze and fag

00:07:52.931 --> 00:07:54.516
'Govt Reformatory'

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:25.589
In a way. only we are
responsible for all this. partner

00:08:25.756 --> 00:08:28.800
When we killed his father
we should have burnt him to ashes too

00:08:29.176 --> 00:08:34.431
Now he has the gall to contest as head
in the Lorry Drivers' Union Election

00:08:35.599 --> 00:08:37.518
How did he amass
this much wealth. bro?

00:08:38.602 --> 00:08:42.189
Logu. do you know how many
lorries run under his control?

00:08:42.898 --> 00:08:45.150
On top of it. he owns a meat factory

00:08:45.150 --> 00:08:46.610
He is into exports too

00:08:46.818 --> 00:08:49.571
All this is common news. partner

00:08:49.863 --> 00:08:52.074
These boys in the reformatory
for juvenile delinquents

00:08:52.115 --> 00:08:54.910
'He uses them to do something
That's where the money flows in'

00:08:54.952 --> 00:08:57.788
Some even say he plays proxy
to a minister to launder his money

00:08:58.163 --> 00:09:01.083
If he wins this year's Union election

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:05.045
...he will stoop to any level
to avenge his father's murder

00:09:05.712 --> 00:09:08.173
Doesn't make sense to spare him
beyond this stage. partner

00:09:20.894 --> 00:09:22.145
Talk of the devil!

00:09:22.187 --> 00:09:23.438
Close his chapter

00:09:45.377 --> 00:09:47.963
Hello. my dear boy
Hindu. Muslim. Christian

00:09:48.005 --> 00:09:50.424
You seem to have the charms
of all the Gods around your neck

00:09:50.465 --> 00:09:51.967
Each sect endorses
a particular God

00:09:52.301 --> 00:09:54.178
One God will save me
when I'm in danger

00:09:54.303 --> 00:09:55.596
Minimum guarantee

00:09:55.637 --> 00:09:56.722
Philosophy?

00:09:57.431 --> 00:10:01.894
Is this the same chap who pleaded
when he was 17 to spare his life?

00:10:04.646 --> 00:10:06.690
We need to discuss something
very important with you

00:10:06.732 --> 00:10:08.901
You were paying us
on a weekly basis all these years

00:10:08.942 --> 00:10:10.360
You can stop it

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:13.447
Instead you can sell all your assets

00:10:13.488 --> 00:10:15.657
'Go and earn a living
somewhere outside India'

00:10:16.074 --> 00:10:18.076
I felt the same and
wanted to tell you next week

00:10:18.118 --> 00:10:19.703
'For how long?
That too every week'

00:10:19.745 --> 00:10:21.955
How can I pay tax to you
to ensure my life is not at risk?

00:10:21.997 --> 00:10:23.749
That's why I've decided
to stop payment

00:10:25.417 --> 00:10:28.587
That decision isn't
yours to take. scumbag!

00:10:28.670 --> 00:10:30.631
'Just zip your lips
and obey our orders'

00:10:30.672 --> 00:10:32.466
I will do only what I feel is right

00:10:32.508 --> 00:10:33.675
Hey...dai!

00:10:33.967 --> 00:10:36.094
I am well aware of
how dirty your hands are

00:10:36.595 --> 00:10:38.931
Making those boys surrender
for the crimes you commit

00:10:38.972 --> 00:10:41.600
'Instigating them to kill
We know about all your offenses'

00:10:41.642 --> 00:10:44.144
Don't show off your temerity
Just tuck your tail and scoot

00:10:44.520 --> 00:10:47.064
Otherwise you will meet your death
in our hands. watch it

00:10:47.105 --> 00:10:49.107
[mocking laughter]

00:10:49.983 --> 00:10:51.360
[imitating laughter]

00:10:51.401 --> 00:10:53.612
Look around you
This is my area

00:10:53.654 --> 00:10:54.821
'If I set my heart on it'

00:10:54.863 --> 00:10:56.490
Only your lorry will move from here

00:10:56.532 --> 00:10:57.658
Not you

00:10:57.699 --> 00:11:01.787
I think you are unable to differentiate
working for money and for gratitude?

00:11:01.954 --> 00:11:03.622
Shall I show you a sample?

00:11:07.167 --> 00:11:09.753
Listen! We have an important
work to do. come here

00:11:11.004 --> 00:11:12.506
'He is calling us. come'

00:11:13.841 --> 00:11:15.926
- 'Bhavani. da
- Why is he calling us suddenly?'

00:11:18.595 --> 00:11:22.391
Whoever kills these 3 men
in this spot will be rewarded

00:11:22.641 --> 00:11:23.934
With a prize money

00:11:25.352 --> 00:11:26.854
2 million

00:11:26.895 --> 00:11:28.647
[burst of amused laughter]

00:11:31.567 --> 00:11:33.861
'Do you realize where you are
and what you are blabbering?'

00:11:33.861 --> 00:11:35.737
You think I work for brother
with money as motive?

00:11:35.821 --> 00:11:37.281
We go back a long way. da

00:11:37.322 --> 00:11:39.366
- 3 million
- If you raise it 50%?

00:11:39.408 --> 00:11:41.410
- 'He is like my own brother'
- 4 million

00:11:41.451 --> 00:11:43.704
Why are you keeping quiet
when he's so arrogant. bro?

00:11:43.787 --> 00:11:44.872
Just say 'yes'
I'll kill him-

00:11:44.913 --> 00:11:45.998
5 million!

00:11:47.833 --> 00:11:49.918
- How dare you rattle off?
- 6 million

00:11:49.960 --> 00:11:51.503
Hey! Kill him now

00:11:51.545 --> 00:11:53.839
Wait...let us hear our brother out!!

00:11:54.715 --> 00:11:56.091
7 million

00:11:56.175 --> 00:11:57.843
Wait...wait. bro

00:11:57.885 --> 00:12:00.804
I'll go up to the gate and
make sure no one enters this area

00:12:00.846 --> 00:12:02.639
- 8 million
- What?

00:12:02.681 --> 00:12:03.807
Move aside

00:12:07.186 --> 00:12:09.354
Then shall we lock
the deal for 8 million?

00:12:09.396 --> 00:12:10.647
- Okay. bro
- Are you ready?

00:12:10.689 --> 00:12:13.066
We will divide 8 million equally
I'll deal with these 3 men

00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:21.366
Now do you know the difference
between greed and gratitude?

00:12:23.076 --> 00:12:24.369
Bro. chopper

00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:32.127
I don't need this

00:12:32.169 --> 00:12:33.879
I'll give you 2 minutes

00:12:33.921 --> 00:12:35.422
Kill me if you can

00:12:37.758 --> 00:12:38.926
And save yourself

00:12:55.150 --> 00:12:56.318
Hey!

00:12:58.695 --> 00:12:59.905
Hey!

00:13:34.189 --> 00:13:35.315
These boys?

00:13:35.691 --> 00:13:36.817
Yes. sir

00:13:38.110 --> 00:13:40.696
Post mortem matches the crime scene?

00:13:40.737 --> 00:13:42.281
They have done a neat job. sir

00:13:42.322 --> 00:13:44.825
Not knowing to drive
they ran over a man

00:13:44.867 --> 00:13:46.285
You expect me to buy this?

00:13:46.326 --> 00:13:47.911
'Whom are you trying to trick?'

00:13:47.953 --> 00:13:49.913
Sir. I'm not a professional driver

00:13:49.955 --> 00:13:52.124
I thought I'll try my hand
But turned out fatal

00:13:52.165 --> 00:13:53.542
- Right?
- Yes. sir

00:13:54.793 --> 00:13:57.171
- 'Do they have a past history?'
- Yes. sir

00:13:57.296 --> 00:13:58.755
Pickpocket case. 511

00:13:58.797 --> 00:14:01.133
Then 6 months they were in
a Govt reformatory

00:14:01.175 --> 00:14:03.427
Now they are in IPC 302
Punished for murder

00:14:03.468 --> 00:14:04.678
Is this a reformatory?

00:14:04.720 --> 00:14:06.430
Or a criminal training center?

00:14:06.680 --> 00:14:09.766
Why do you need this reformatory
that turns a thief into a murderer?

00:14:10.100 --> 00:14:12.436
- Call the Observation home staff
- Okay. sir

00:14:12.811 --> 00:14:14.354
Sir. he's calling you

00:14:15.814 --> 00:14:18.150
Good afternoon. sir
I am the superintendent here

00:14:18.150 --> 00:14:21.111
Forget the introduction. when do you
intend employing a regular master?

00:14:21.153 --> 00:14:24.072
The boys drive away
any master we appoint

00:14:24.114 --> 00:14:26.617
Actually scared of them.
no teacher wants to take up this post

00:14:26.783 --> 00:14:28.118
But how can you run a school?

00:14:28.160 --> 00:14:29.953
'Not one teacher so far. huh?'

00:14:30.454 --> 00:14:32.122
Shocking and shameful!

00:14:32.956 --> 00:14:36.418
If there's no master to teach
or guide the students

00:14:36.460 --> 00:14:38.337
'...how will they reform. huh?'

00:14:38.378 --> 00:14:41.548
'I have personally seen
30-40 cases like this here'

00:14:41.924 --> 00:14:43.884
'Superintendent. I'm passing a Govt order'

00:14:43.926 --> 00:14:47.596
'Send it to all private. Govt schools
and colleges. to every single institution'

00:14:47.638 --> 00:14:48.889
Whole of Tamil Nadu

00:14:48.931 --> 00:14:51.350
'You'll find a master
for sure. understand?'

00:14:51.642 --> 00:14:52.935
Type out the order

00:15:00.817 --> 00:15:03.737
"They call me master
Changes will happen faster"

00:15:10.452 --> 00:15:11.411
"His entry spells power"

00:15:11.453 --> 00:15:12.829
"Who is our master?
Commander...!"

00:15:12.871 --> 00:15:15.832
'St Jeffery College is a truly renowned
educational institution in Chennai'

00:15:15.874 --> 00:15:17.835
'Alumni of this college
have carved a name'

00:15:17.876 --> 00:15:21.922
'In cinema. politics. advertising and
are celebrities in their own might'

00:15:21.964 --> 00:15:24.424
This college has molded innumerable VIPs

00:15:24.466 --> 00:15:30.138
'Students are very eager to make this
a very memorable reunion'

00:15:30.347 --> 00:15:32.474
Do you want to know why?
Come along with me

00:15:35.477 --> 00:15:36.728
Hi...Ramya

00:15:36.937 --> 00:15:38.730
- Hi. nice to meet you
- Same here

00:15:38.814 --> 00:15:40.440
I've spoken to you over the phone

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:41.650
- Oh! That was you?
- Yeah

00:15:41.650 --> 00:15:42.818
Okay...okay

00:15:42.860 --> 00:15:45.070
- What's your full name?
- Charulatha Prasad

00:15:45.070 --> 00:15:47.573
Come. let me introduce you to everyone

00:15:47.614 --> 00:15:50.617
- This college has a decorum
- Students are capable of doing it

00:15:50.659 --> 00:15:53.745
Their plan is to ruin our image when
the minister arrives as our chief guest

00:15:53.787 --> 00:15:56.331
'If this issue leaks.
your college reputation is at stake'

00:15:56.373 --> 00:15:58.500
You want to take further action

00:15:58.542 --> 00:16:00.752
- Do so after the minister leaves
- This is well planned

00:16:00.794 --> 00:16:02.713
'Sri. stop this cat & mouse game'

00:16:02.754 --> 00:16:05.132
- You had better confess the truth
- Trust me. sir

00:16:05.174 --> 00:16:06.925
- Isn't JD responsible?
- No. sir

00:16:06.967 --> 00:16:08.135
I swear. no. sir

00:16:08.177 --> 00:16:10.596
Then who is the culprit?
Your father...?

00:16:10.846 --> 00:16:12.764
Everyone knows about Savitha's trauma

00:16:12.806 --> 00:16:14.850
I know how those 2 scumbags
sexually harassed her-

00:16:14.933 --> 00:16:16.143
Hey! Mind your words

00:16:16.185 --> 00:16:17.603
Spit that gum first

00:16:19.813 --> 00:16:20.814
I said throw it out

00:16:20.898 --> 00:16:22.608
I'll trash it as soon as
it loses its sweetness

00:16:22.816 --> 00:16:23.901
Don't act smart

00:16:24.359 --> 00:16:26.153
The two noble souls
who sexually harassed her

00:16:26.320 --> 00:16:27.863
You suspended them for 1 week

00:16:27.905 --> 00:16:30.407
Knowing it was inadequate
we even complained to the police

00:16:30.449 --> 00:16:32.826
But they took us for a ride
without taking any action

00:16:32.868 --> 00:16:35.078
Only then we knew Aadith's dad
is a rich businessman

00:16:35.120 --> 00:16:37.497
I think he has planned
to send them off to Canada

00:16:37.623 --> 00:16:39.416
That's why I took the boys

00:16:39.458 --> 00:16:41.168
'...to his house
to find out his plan'

00:16:43.462 --> 00:16:45.714
'Hello. sir. they haven't
left the house as yet'

00:16:45.756 --> 00:16:47.007
'I think they are still inside'

00:16:47.049 --> 00:16:49.718
'But it's evident they have
hatched a plot to escape'

00:16:49.801 --> 00:16:52.471
'Strangers keep walking in to their house'

00:16:52.513 --> 00:16:54.806
'Sir. I can hear their voices
I think they are coming out'

00:16:54.848 --> 00:16:56.433
- 'Take care. son
- Don't worry. pa'

00:16:56.475 --> 00:16:58.852
- Be safe
- I'll call as soon as I reach

00:16:58.894 --> 00:17:00.354
'This is the duo'

00:17:00.395 --> 00:17:01.605
'Call after you reach the airport'

00:17:01.813 --> 00:17:02.856
Go...go...go

00:17:03.649 --> 00:17:04.816
Let's follow them

00:17:06.860 --> 00:17:08.946
Both of them have left home. sir

00:17:08.987 --> 00:17:11.406
Aadith and Rahul are in a taxi
They just crossed Ashok Nagar

00:17:11.448 --> 00:17:13.700
'Along with our boys
I am following them. sir'

00:17:13.742 --> 00:17:15.327
- Where are you. bro?
- 'At a signal'

00:17:15.369 --> 00:17:17.579
- Which signal?
- Jafferkhanpet

00:17:17.621 --> 00:17:18.747
Ask him the bus number

00:17:19.164 --> 00:17:20.332
- Which bus?
- '70 V'

00:17:20.374 --> 00:17:21.375
Bus number. bro?

00:17:21.416 --> 00:17:22.751
70. V

00:17:22.793 --> 00:17:24.753
It's coming close to you
Waiting at the signal now

00:17:24.795 --> 00:17:26.088
'Bro...look this side'

00:17:26.129 --> 00:17:27.673
I've spotted you Come on. hurry up

00:17:27.714 --> 00:17:29.174
'Look. it's that bus'

00:17:29.299 --> 00:17:30.467
Quick!

00:17:34.930 --> 00:17:36.515
- 'Get in'
- Move

00:17:36.557 --> 00:17:38.433
Both of them got into
bus number 70 V. sir

00:17:38.475 --> 00:17:40.811
'Bus number TN 01 AN 1184'

00:17:40.853 --> 00:17:43.146
'Bus has crossed
Jafferkhanpet signa-'

00:17:43.814 --> 00:17:45.315
Why did he cut my call?

00:17:47.693 --> 00:17:50.153
"Got the man with the plan right here"

00:17:50.320 --> 00:17:52.447
"Bringin' swag with the man right here"

00:17:52.489 --> 00:17:54.616
[mobile ringing]

00:17:54.825 --> 00:17:57.119
