01:45:11.061 --> 01:45:13.438
"Don't get into his bad books. stay away"

01:45:13.480 --> 01:45:14.940
"Master's raid
All crimes waylaid"

01:45:14.982 --> 01:45:16.149
"Master's raid. da!"

01:45:16.149 --> 01:45:18.610
"A-Aa-E-Ee. A-B-C-D
