I'm so mad I feel like sta-

01:45:49.516 --> 01:45:51.185
'I feel like stabbing him right now'

01:45:51.226 --> 01:45:53.604
When you get your hands dirty
enemies will come and go

01:45:53.645 --> 01:45:56.940
